name: douyin makeup
description:
This model is best used with weight 0.8-1.0. Your image might be blurred if the weight is too high.

Because this embedding is trained on photos, it tends to produce realistic faces. However, it also works well with anime style model, just use prompt like cute loli face to keep the 2d style.

note that the example images are generated with xformer, so the seed will not be deterministic.
